--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 INDEX
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 
 1. Installation

 1-1 Configuration
 1-2 Compiling with gcc
 1-3 Using with eggdrop 
 1-4 Cryptic errors



--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 1-1 Configuration
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Edit dZSbconf.tcl ... nothing else :)


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 1-2 Compiling with gcc
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Change dir to extra, run 'make all'.. keep your fingers crossed... done
 Now copy these files to /glftpd/bin/:
 bnctest.sh - if you want a functioning bnc tester :)
 incomplete-list.sh - if you want a functioning !inc-trigger
 passchk - if you want a functioning !invite
 (the rest are for additional features that are not directly linked to
  this script, like invite.sh is for a "site invite" command etc, read
  comments in scripts to find out more)


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 1-3 Using with eggdrop
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Just load it with other scripts and you're done. Remeber to
 put the dZSbconf.tcl in the same dir as the script.


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 1-4 Cryptic errors
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 "You didn't sacrifice a lamb like you were told, did you?"
  - read 1-3, you need to put dZSbconf.tcl in the proper location! ;)
 "Blood has been spilled this night. (<something>)"
  - the binary specified in 'set binary(<something>)' does not exist or is not
    executable by the eggdrop.
